claim: Latin pop entered the U.S. music scene with the help of Ricky Martin.
premise_source_doc_sentence: In early 1999 , after releasing several albums in Spanish , Martin performed `` The Cup of Life '' at the 41st Grammy Awards show , which became a catalyst in bringing Latin pop to the forefront of the U.S. music scene .

claim: Latin pop entered the U.S. music scene with the help of Ricky Martin.
